race.description: Picklebet Get Your Pickle On Handicap (Bm56)
race.comment: THINKING SENSATION (7) stayed out of trouble and led all the way to win his maiden at Donald in his penultimate start, and then held that form when finishing second at Yarra Valley just over 3 weeks ago when sent out as the favourite. The slight drop back in trip will suit him, and he will be hard to beat again. SUZE SPRITZ (12) won her maiden by a length here 2 starts back, and then was beaten by a wide draw as the favourite last time out at Terang 10 days ago. She is still at the improving stage of her career, and from a slightly better gate, she can bounce straight back into the money here. YAKI ISHI (1) did nothing fresh up, and then charged home at big odds second up when finishing runner-up at Echuca 12 days ago. The extra 220m is ideal, and he can go one better, but don't expect another fancy price. IZOLA (11) resumes from a spell, and any market leads are worth following. SHOWMARA (3) is worth another chance with a senior hoop back in the saddle.
